Get a new mail on any SMTP service (Here we will use Gmail)

- Make sure u have configured 2-Step Verification in order to get the App Passwords setting.
- Goto Manage Account -> Security -> Signing in to Google -> App Passwords
- Select Mail and Other. Generate the Password and Save it somewhere

## Connecting the NodeMailer

- Create a Transport Object
- Using this object create a function which can send mail
- Use that function to send mail

## Cron Jobs: Scheduled Jobs
- node-cron
